Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵達守護翼的酷一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上層人物的干預下被迫與蕾分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.89,0:02:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並被告知不可能再見到蕾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面 沉浸在煌珠樂園的幻影中的蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也在自稱伊芙的神密人物的指引下回到了現實世界中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.63,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混亂之中 決定獨自一人前往煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.85,0:02:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與此同時 知道了這一情況的酷離開了守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.78,0:02:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年和少女能再次相遇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.71,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑借防禦屬性探測煌珠的所在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對絕對能幫上你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作需要你的這種能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.14,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四唱 煌珠獵人、再度來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 不是說好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我帶你去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你居然一個人走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 我一定會去找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫魯斯輔佐官 請解釋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨夜的戰鬥究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷被人襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不僅如此 守護翼總部居然受到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳細情況現在正在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再具體的就不能告訴你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.67,0:04:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方真的是叫做ChaosChoir的組織嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我再問一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.76,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要分開酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂和莉莉雅兩人生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是酷和蕾卻沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾也不在城裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白身為七煌寶樹的蕾是個特殊的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但做到這份上就太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他們說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶他們去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.46,0:05:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不但違背了和他們的約定還把他們強制隔離開來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這和欺騙他們沒什麼區別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的是保護煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道所做的一切不是為了保護她們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的舉措也是以此為理念而採取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是守護翼民意決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 蕾現在在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也正在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就把這個任務交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.34,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾 搜索任務已經交由別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指定的獵物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼接下來的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方法隨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡快回收她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 守護翼不也和我們獵人一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 工作的事情談完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.67,0:06:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會非常非常努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和臥魯合作的話不管什麼工作都能輕鬆搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只不過是道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別廢話任我使喚就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.11,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然知道乘火車到了這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 你到底在哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你已不在這城市了嗎 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就老老實實地回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆真是沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你那麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各自房裏待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是庫魯斯輔佐官的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管方式如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼保護煌珠這一理念是沒有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管他庫魯斯啊守護翼啊這樣那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說實話那些根本不用加以理睬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 你想怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷可是毫不猶豫地衝出去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想見他們倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見到了想跟他們道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想去就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想去就不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼簡單的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和前輩的心情一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有庫魯斯輔佐官的命令在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.58,0:09:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休假申請啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些孩子也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.02,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在接到下一個命令之前拿到休假就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得你這麼聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是我教導有方的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是總覺得有點太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 喂 看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我的裝備樣式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 庫魯斯輔佐官他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.14,0:09:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然那位大人比誰都更理解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這正是愛的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就是命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.63,0:09:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫魯斯輔佐官 希絲卡 希絲卡我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍 快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.89,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有制服有時會更方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一路小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 小氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我坐一下又有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世道艱辛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都無視我走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還得快點追上蕾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好勒 這次一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 載我去鄰村好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.19,0:10:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指蕾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你要找蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.86,0:10:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是煌珠獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盯上獵物是理所應當的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不巧的是 蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不巧的是 我不會把蕾輕易交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你同契了的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就先把你解決了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 附近沒有煌珠的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是先問出她的下落為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別對我指手畫腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然來這一套啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵物就要全力追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我勸你還是快點同契為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那東西是七煌寶樹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你連這個也知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不同尋常的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.95,0:11:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為和那東西同契了 你才能活到現在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別張口閉口「那東西」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾可不是物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那東西就是物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為戰鬥而存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是武器而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽見我說不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種對手我一個人就足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.13,0:12:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙 絕對不能把蕾交給那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,福音響起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的小命我拿下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 果然很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,附近沒有煌珠的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武器竟敢對我指手畫腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,替代你的道具是要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你 你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸根到底還不是把那女孩當武器或道具來用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然的確和蕾多次同契一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使沒有戰鬥我也想待在蕾的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想讓蕾陪在我的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道沒有這樣的想法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道具終究只是道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是在使用這東西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.37,0:13:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些煌珠們就是為了被我們使用才存在著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別無其它活下去的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有蹤影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多應該追上酷了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那邊 看那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這輛摩托車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我交給酷的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.54,0:14:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們兵分兩路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還是逃不掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許應該想個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那傢伙不跟我交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有七煌寶樹這樣的武器卻為何...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 冷靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓我一再重複
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.49,0:14:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還想過那樣的日子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說過了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用那女孩這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是只憑自己的力量就戰鬥不了的傢伙的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要靠我自己的實力打敗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯 小心上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡 你怎麼會在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這話應該我說才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為你離開守護翼去追趕蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到竟然在這種地方和煌珠獵人打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他追著我不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你手腳笨拙也是一個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真幹得了空賊這一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.72,0:16:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追究起來難道不是你們把我和蕾分開才惹出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那個的確如你所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.09,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說好能讓你們在一起的卻弄成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借口就不找了 真的是太對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這和那是兩回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.89,0:16:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我們提前半天跑出來為什麼還在這裏瞎轉悠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又迷路了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是想要幹什麼 道歉還是教訓我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩者都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好豎起耳朵聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是一次又一次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不錯的作戰方案啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你們還真是有緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 應該機緣巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉露露 同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再跟我同契一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已經沒有同契的力氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能戰鬥的話就沒你什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再去找個代替品罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類 人類就那麼了不起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.02,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有資格把保護你的煌珠叫做物體嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把物體叫做物體有什麼不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用的道具只會生銹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.12,0:18:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用到壞掉為止才是這些傢伙們的夙願吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是人類自私的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你們守護翼又如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管以什麼為借口 所作所為不也和我沒多大區別嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.09,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在保護的名義下隔離煌珠 剝奪她們的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的你們沒有資格來否定我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.51,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是因為有你這樣的人存在我們才必須保護煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們並不是什麼武器或物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了創造能和守護者共存的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以守護翼的名義與你戰鬥到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你怎麼狡辯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠是道具這一事實是不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼現在你能安然無恙卻又是為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠是給人使用的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我就在此把你打倒為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯由我來保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你們碰他一根手指的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是道具或武器都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為臥魯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.16,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯說了需要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要保護臥魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對絕對要保護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是那孩子贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 沒想到你們都會追上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不就是違抗了命令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正式請假過了
