Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那已成了悲傷之谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天空的少年啊
